7 An Act relating to county fairs; creating the County
Fair Modernization Act; requiring members of the
8 County Free Fair Association Board of Directors must
meet attendance requirement; clarifying that members
9 who do not meet attendance requirement will cease to
hold office; permitting members to take recommended
10 training course; providing for noncodification;
providing for codification; and providing an
11 effective date.
