13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
16 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
17 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "County Fair
18 Modernization Act".
19 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 15-97 of Title 2, unless there
21 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 Whenever a member of the County Free Fair Association Board of
23 Directors is absent from more than fifty percent (50%) of all
24 meetings of the Board, regular and special, held within any period
