1 of f our consecutive meetings, that member shall thereupon cease to
2 hold office, and that position shall be considered vacant.
3 SECTION 3. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
4 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 15-98 of Title 2, unless there
5 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
6 Members of the County Free Fair Association Board may take a
7 recommended training course offered by Oklahoma State University's
8 extension office, delivered online, to better serve in their elected
9 position.
10 SECTION 4. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
